data.description: **New, gorgeous LVP flooring recently installed** Welcome to this charming bungalow home nestled in Riverside. This delightful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is a true gem, freshly painted walls that are stunningly accented by all of the natural light. Step inside and prepare to be amazed by the stunning kitchen, with stylish white cabinets, complemented by sleek light fixtures, this space will inspire your inner chef. While exploring, you'll discover the beautiful hardwood floors that flow throughout, providing warmth and elegance to every room. The open concept layout creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining. The bedrooms are generously sized, ensuring everyone has their own peaceful retreat to unwind. And don't forget the cute backyard, where you can enjoy outdoor gatherings. Schedule a showing today!
